%F A000261 For offset -1: (1/6)*Sum_{k=0..n} (-1)^k*(n-k+1)*(n-k+2)*(n-k+3)*n!/k! = (1/6)*(A000166(n)+3*A000166(n+1)+3*A000166(n+2)+A000166(n+3)). - _Vladeta Jovovic_, Jan 07 2003
